description:
A Chaos lost could drop her from the top 16 and out of the SUMMER VENGEANCE event this summer. Her season could be over. Does she have what it takes to win or will her season end by getting fucked and used on the mat.
The Assassin showed great promise in her last match defeating a veteran; she is ranked in the top 10 and with a win hopes to improve her draw in the SUMMER VENGEANCE tournament this summer.
title: The Assassin(1-2) Ranked 9th
